The most adorable thing so far in 2020 is soccer player Teko Modise and his new wife, Lerato Kgamanyane. The couple secretly wedded back in 2018. The  mega soccer star affectionately refers to his wife as "Berries" and she is constant feature on Teko’s social media. The cute couple has been serving us couple goals with their cute outfits on their baecation. They recently came back from a romantic getaway in Bali. It's no secret that Teko is head of over heels as he publicly declared that she has changed his world. This is not Teko’s first marriage, he was married to Felicia Modise, who was on Diski Diva’s after their divorce. He was also engaged to social media influencer and entrepreneur Lizelle Tabane. 